    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Poems with six stanzas of six lines each. The last words of the first stanza are repeated, in a different order, in the other five stanzas. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
